::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Reptilica and DevilDuer walk into the bridge of the Alliance base, Reptilica 
glancing at the scanners.

"Hey! There's a bot sending out a beacon there!" he says, pointing at the 
screen. DevilDuer also looks, grinning. "Sounds like it want to join us, Rep!"

Reptilica frowns. "Let's go check it out. And don't call me Rep, Devil."

DevilDuer grins, following Reptilica out the door. Reaching the exit, 
Reptilica activates his jetpack, flying off toward Feline as DevilDuer runs 
to catch up.
